                </div>

                <div style="padding:2rem;">
                    <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-indigo-400 dark:text-orange-400">What we do</p>
                    <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-neutral-100">
                        Four disciplines, one partner
                    </p>
