                        Workflow, integration, AI and reporting automation, all under one roof.
                    </p>
                </div>

            </div>

            <!-- MIDDLE: Two stacked cards -->
            <div style="flex:1; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:12px;">

                <!-- Bespoke — count-up added -->
                <div class="bg-white dark:bg-neutral-900 ring-1 ring-slate-200 dark:ring-white/5"
                     style="flex:1; border-radius:18px; overflow:hidden;
                    display:flex; flex-direction:column;">

                    <div class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-neutral-800"
                         style="height:160px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;">
                        <div style="text-align:center; padding:0 2rem;">
                            <p class="text-indigo-400 dark:text-orange-400" style="font-size:64px; font-weight:500; line-height:1;">
                                <span id="about-percent">0</span>%
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-neutral-400" style="margin-top:8px;">
                                Bespoke. No templates, no guesswork.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div style="padding:1.5rem 2rem;">
                        <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-indigo-400 dark:text-orange-400">Our approach</p>
                        <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-neutral-100">
                            Built around your business
                        </p>
                    </div>

                </div>

                <!-- Location — pulsating rings added -->
                <div class="bg-white dark:bg-neutral-900 ring-1 ring-slate-200 dark:ring-white/5"
                     style="flex:1; border-radius:18px; overflow:hidden;
                    display:flex; flex-direction:column;">

                    <div class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-neutral-800"
                         style="height:160px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;">
                        <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; gap:16px;">

                            <div style="position:relative; width:64px; height:64px;
                                display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;">

                                <div class="animate-ping rounded-full ring-1 ring-indigo-400/20 dark:ring-orange-400/20"
                                     style="position:absolute; width:64px; height:64px;
                                            animation-duration:2.4s;"></div>

                                <div class="animate-ping rounded-full ring-1 ring-indigo-400/30 dark:ring-orange-400/30"
                                     style="position:absolute; width:44px; height:44px;
                                            animation-duration:1.8s; animation-delay:0.4s;"></div>

                                <div class="bg-indigo-400/10 dark:bg-orange-400/10 ring-1 ring-indigo-400/40 dark:ring-orange-400/40 rounded-full"
                                     style="width:28px; height:28px; display:flex;
                                    align-items:center; justify-content:center;">
                                    <span class="rounded-full bg-green-500"
                                          style="width:8px; height:8px; display:block;"></span>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:6px;">
                                <span class="rounded-full bg-green-500"
                                      style="width:6px; height:6px; flex-shrink:0; display:block;"></span>
                                <span class="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-neutral-400">
                                    Remote-first. Always reachable.
                                </span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div style="padding:1.5rem 2rem;">
                        <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-indigo-400 dark:text-orange-400">UK-wide</p>
                        <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-neutral-100">
                            Based in Keswick, working everywhere
                        </p>
                    </div>

                </div>

            </div>

            <!-- RIGHT: Pipeline -->
            <div class="bg-white dark:bg-neutral-900 ring-1 ring-slate-200 dark:ring-white/5"
                 style="width:300px; flex-shrink:0; border-radius:18px; overflow:hidden;
                display:flex; flex-direction:column;">

                <div class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-neutral-800"
                     style="height:300px; display:flex; align-items:center;
                    justify-content:center; padding:2rem;">

                    <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:flex-start; width:100%;">

                        <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px;">
                            <div class="bg-white dark:bg-neutral-900 ring-1 ring-slate-200 dark:ring-white/5"
                                 style="width:36px; height:36px; border-radius:10px; flex-shrink:0;
                                display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;">
